'''马乔丽·泰勒·格林'''（{{lang-en|Marjorie Taylor Greene}}，{{bd|1974年|5月21日}}）是美国[[政治人物|政客]]、[[商人|商人]]，被{{who|有些人}}认为是[[阴谋论|阴谋论者]]，是[[乔治亚州第十四国会选区|乔治亚州第十四国会选区]]的现任[[美国众议员|美国众议员]]<ref>{{cite news|last=Levin|first=Sam|url=https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2020/nov/03/qanon-marjorie-taylor-greene-wins-congress|title=QAnon supporter Marjorie Taylor Greene wins seat in US House|work=The Guardian|date=2020-11-04|access-date=2021-01-09|archive-date=2020-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201104030953/https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2020/nov/03/qanon-marjorie-taylor-greene-wins-congress|dead-url=no}}</ref>。格林的政治立场被认为是[[极右翼|极右翼]]<ref>{{cite news |last1=Stanley-Becker |last2=Bade |first1=Isaac |first2=Rachel |title=QAnon supporter, with Georgia primary victory, is poised to bring far-right conspiracy theory to Congress |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/2020/08/11/marjorie-taylor-greene-georgia-qanon/ |access-date=2021-01-09 |date=2020-08-11 |newspaper=The Washington Post}}</ref>，她曾在[[Facebook|Facebook]]视频中表达了对极右翼阴谋论[[匿名者Q|匿名者Q]]的支持，但后来试图与阴谋论远离<ref name="qanon" /> 。

==早年生活==
格林于1974年5月27日出生于[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]]的[[米利奇维尔|米利奇维尔]]<ref>{{Cite news|last=Rodrigo|first=Chris Mills|date=2020-11-30|title=Rep.-elect Marjorie Taylor Greene (R-Ga.-14)|url=https://thehill.com/new-members-guide-2020/527754-rep-elect-marjorie-taylor-greene-r-ga-14|access-date=2021-01-09|work=The Hill|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203162025/https://thehill.com/new-members-guide-2020/527754-rep-elect-marjorie-taylor-greene-r-ga-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她毕业于乔治亚州[[卡明_(佐治亚州)|卡明]]的{{le|南福赛斯高中|South Forsyth High School}}<ref>{{Cite web|title=Marjorie Taylor Greene: How an Outspoken MAGA Fan Built a Following in a World of Extremists|url=https://www.splcenter.org/hatewatch/2019/08/16/marjorie-taylor-greene-how-outspoken-maga-fan-built-following-world-extremists|date=2019-08-16|access-date=2021-01-09|website=Southern Poverty Law Center|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812162917/https://www.splcenter.org/hatewatch/2019/08/16/marjorie-taylor-greene-how-outspoken-maga-fan-built-following-world-extremists|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[乔治亚大学|乔治亚大学]]，获得[[工商管理学士|工商管理学士]]学位<ref name="Rolling Stone">{{cite news |last1=Dickson |first1=E. J. |title=Marjorie Taylor Greene, Trump's Favorite QAnon Candidate, Wins Georgia Primary |url=https://www.rollingstone.com/politics/politics-news/marjorie-taylor-greene-georgia-qanon-congress-1043129/ |accessdate=2021-01-09 |work=Rolling Stone |date=2020-08-12 |archive-date=2020-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201102133854/https://www.rollingstone.com/politics/politics-news/marjorie-taylor-greene-georgia-qanon-congress-1043129/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。格林创立、发展并后来出售了美国顶尖的[[混合健身|混合健身]]健身馆之一<ref name="FXStabil11092020">{{cite news |title=13 GOP women join the House, dominating congressional elections, making history |url=https://www.foxnews.com/politics/13-gop-women-joining-the-house-to-dominate-congressional-elections |date=2020-11-09 |last=Stabile |first=Angelica |work=Fox News |accessdate=2021-01-09 |archive-date=2020-11-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201122170901/https://www.foxnews.com/politics/13-gop-women-joining-the-house-to-dominate-congressional-elections |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==美国众议院==
===选举===
====2020年大选====
格林于2020年开始竞选[[乔治亚州第六国会选区|乔治亚州第六国会选区]]的议员，但在现任议员[[汤姆·格拉维斯|汤姆·格拉维斯]]宣布不再竞选连任后，她将竞选活动转移到了[[乔治亚州第十四国会选区|第十四选区]]<ref>{{cite news |last=Stilwell |first=Don |url=https://www.mdjonline.com/neighbor_newspapers/news/state/marjorie-greene-officially-shifts-campaign-to-district-congressional-seat/article_2cad8023-f01c-5c2b-a9ff-33447520a498.html |title=Marjorie Greene officially shifts campaign to District 14 congressional seat {{!}} Georgia News |newspaper=Marietta Daily Journal|date=2019-12-13 |accessdate=2021-01-10 |archive-date=2020-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200208054911/https://www.mdjonline.com/neighbor_newspapers/news/state/marjorie-greene-officially-shifts-campaign-to-district-congressional-seat/article_2cad8023-f01c-5c2b-a9ff-33447520a498.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她竞选的口号是“拯救美国，停止[[社会主义|社会主义]]”（{{lang|en|Save America, Stop Socialism}}）<ref name=":2" /><ref name=":3">{{Cite web|last=Kuznia|first=Rob|last2=Richards|first2=Collette|last3=Griffin|first3=Drew|date=2020-09-23|title=Congressional candidate's apparent ascent to Congress could be a 'bellwether' for QAnon|url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/09/23/politics/marjorie-taylor-greene-qanon-congress-invs/index.html|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031231506/https://www.cnn.com/2020/09/23/politics/marjorie-taylor-greene-qanon-congress-invs/index.html|archive-date=2020-10-31|access-date=2021-01-10|website=CNN}}</ref>。在初选前几天，[[Facebook|Facebook]]以违反其条款为由删除了格林的上传的一段视频。在视频中，她手持一把{{le|AR-15型步枪|AR-15 style rifle}}，警告“[[反法西斯主义运动_(美国)|安提法]]恐怖分子”要“远离乔治亚西北部”<ref name=":2">{{cite news |url=https://www.timesfreepress.com/news/local/story/2020/jun/05/facebook-deletes-marjorie-greene-ad-inciting/524666/ |title=Facebook deletes Georgia congressional candidate Marjorie Greene's ad |work=Chattanooga Times Free Press|first=Patrick |last=Filbin |date=2020-06-05 |access-date=2021-01-10 |archive-date=2020-09-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200917004626/https://www.timesfreepress.com/news/local/story/2020/jun/05/facebook-deletes-marjorie-greene-ad-inciting/524666/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

格林在共和党初选中排名第一，在党内决选中与约翰·科恩对决<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.northwestgeorgianews.com/calhoun_times/marjorie-greene-john-cowan-likely-headed-for-runoff-in-georgias-14th-congressional-district/article_fd3b400e-ab27-11ea-bc3e-d7ad0cb56b48.html |title=Marjorie Greene, John Cowan likely headed for runoff in Georgia's 14th Congressional District |newspaper=The Calhoun Times |agency=Capitol Beat News Service |first=Beau |last=Evans |date=2020-06-10 |accessdate=2021-01-10 |archive-date=2020-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200611055834/https://www.northwestgeorgianews.com/calhoun_times/marjorie-greene-john-cowan-likely-headed-for-runoff-in-georgias-14th-congressional-district/article_fd3b400e-ab27-11ea-bc3e-d7ad0cb56b48.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。8月11日，格林击败了科恩，赢得了提名。格林被认为是赢得大选席位的压倒性热门人选，因为第十四选区通常都是共和党人的稳定票仓<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/08/11/us/politics/marjorie-taylor-greene-qanon-georgia-primary.html|title=Marjorie Taylor Greene, a QAnon Supporter, Wins House Primary in Georgia|first1=Matthew|last1=Rosenberg|first2=Astead W.|last2=Herndon|first3=Nick|last3=Corasaniti|date=2020-08-11|access-date=2021-01-10|work=The New York Times|archive-date=2020-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812060224/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/08/11/us/politics/marjorie-taylor-greene-qanon-georgia-primary.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。第十四选区的[[库克党派投票指数|库克党派投票指数]]为R+27，在全美排名第十，在东部时区排名第三。在乔治亚州的国会选区中，只有邻近的{{le|乔治亚州第九国会选区|Georgia's 9th congressional district|第九选区}}更具共和党色彩。2016年[[唐纳德·特朗普|唐纳德·特朗普]]在第十四选区赢得以75%的得票率，这是他在全美第八强的表现<ref>{{cite web |url=https://cookpolitical.com/pvi-map-and-district-list |title=Cook Partisan Voting Index |accessdate=2021-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200904082835/https://cookpolitical.com/pvi-map-and-district-list |archive-date=2020-09-04}} for the 116th Congress</ref>。在格林决选获胜后的第二天，特朗普在[[推特|推特]]上表示支持她，形容格林是一个“共和党未来之星”，“在每件事上都很坚强，从不放弃——一个真正的赢家！” <ref>{{cite news|last=Cohen|first=Max|url=https://www.politico.com/news/2020/08/12/trump-georgia-qanon-taylor-greene-394204|title=Trump calls Georgia GOP candidate who embraces QAnon a 'future Republican Star'|work=Politico|date=2020-08-12|access-date=2021-01-10|archive-date=2020-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200907171705/https://www.politico.com/news/2020/08/12/trump-georgia-qanon-taylor-greene-394204|dead-url=no}}</ref>

格林最初预计将面对民主党IT专家凯文·范·奥斯达尔，但他在2020年9月11日退出了竞选，这使得格林在大选中没有对手。该选区的共和党人非常多，如果奥斯达尔继续竞选，他将面临几乎不可能的胜算<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.ajc.com/politics/politics-blog/why-marjorie-taylor-greenes-opponent-quit-the-house-race/E3TYSMAAPRDUPPB6F3BBQAFCME/ |title=Why Marjorie Taylor Greene's opponent quit the House race |first1=Greg |last1=Bluestein |newspaper=The Atlanta Journal-Constitution |date=2020-09-12 |access-date=2021-01-10 |archive-date=2020-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200912105042/https://www.ajc.com/politics/politics-blog/why-marjorie-taylor-greenes-opponent-quit-the-house-race/E3TYSMAAPRDUPPB6F3BBQAFCME/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。自2012年选举以来，没有民主党人在十四选区赢得超过30%的选票<ref>{{cite web |title=GA - District 14 - History |url=https://www.ourcampaigns.com/ContainerHistory.html?ContainerID=142218 |website=Our Campaigns |accessdate=2021-01-10 |archive-date=2020-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027024745/https://www.ourcampaigns.com/ContainerHistory.html?ContainerID=142218 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在大选中，格林以74%的得票率获胜。奥斯达尔的名字仍然留在选票上，他获得了25%的选票<ref>{{cite news |title=Georgia 2020 election results |url=https://www.cnn.com/election/2020/results/state/georgia |access-date=2021-01-10 |work=CNN |language=en}}</ref>。格林成为第二位在众议院代表乔治亚州的共和党女性。第一位是{{le|凯伦·汉德尔|Karen Handel}}，她在{{le|2017年乔治亚州第六国会选区特别选举|2017 Georgia's 6th congressional district special election|2017年特别选举}}中当选为[[乔治亚州第六国会选区|第六选区]]国会议员<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.cnn.com/2017/06/21/politics/karen-handel-first-gop-woman-rep-congress-wins/index.html|title=Handel first female GOP rep elected to Congress in Georgia|first1=Sophie|last1=Tatum|work=CNN|date=2017-06-21|access-date=2021-01-10|archive-date=2017-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171111213803/http://www.cnn.com/2017/06/21/politics/karen-handel-first-gop-woman-rep-congress-wins/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但在2018年的完整任期选举中被击败。因此，格林成为第一位在乔治亚州国会选区当选完整任期的共和党女性。

===任期===
[[File:Marjorie_Taylor_Greene_swearing_in.jpg|thumb]]宣誓就职]]
在格林上任的第一天，她戴着一个口罩站在众议院内，上面写着“特朗普赢了”（{{lang|en|Trump Won}}）<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.wttw.com/2021/01/04/many-more-gop-rejecting-trumps-bid-undo-his-defeat|title=Many More in GOP Rejecting Trump’s Bid To Undo His Defeat|publisher=WTTW|date=2021-01-04|accessdate=2021-01-10}}</ref>。在{{le|2021年美国选举人团计票|2021 United States Electoral College count|计票过程}}中，格林提出了反对计统计[[密歇根州|密歇根州]]的选票。然而，反对意见没有[[美国参议院|参议院]]的一名成员签署，因此无效<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cnn.com/politics/live-news/congress-electoral-college-vote-count-2021/h_d1a4ed65d72d2d179b6de0489e1df9a8|title=GOP bid to object to Michigan's electoral result fails|publisher=[[有線電視新聞網|有線電視新聞網]]|date=2021-01-07|accessdate=2021-01-10}}</ref>。

为了回应2021年1月6日[[2021年美国国会大厦遭冲击事件|国会大厦遭冲击事件]]，格林呼吁结束暴力，支持特朗普总统<ref name="LBmrR">{{cite news |title=Georgia lawmakers, officials condemn violent protests at U.S. Capitol |url=https://www.wsbtv.com/news/local/atlanta/georgia-lawmakers-officials-condemn-violent-protests-us-capitol/BCHIPQMTVRBIJHOWS4MB4DVVRU/ |access-date=2021-01-29 |work=WSBTV |date=2021-01-06}}</ref>。暴乱期间，她在原地避难时拒绝戴口罩，在[[第二次特朗普弹劾案|罢免总统的辩论]]中，她在推特上写道，“民主党人必须为他们的言论引发的政治暴力负责。”这促使民主党众议员{{le|杰森·克劳|Jason Crow}}称她为“道德败坏”、“堕落”和“坦率地说很危险”<ref name="XnFLV">{{cite news |last1=Forgey |first1=Quint |title='Depraved': Rep. Jason Crow condemns Rep. Marjorie Taylor Greene's rhetoric ahead of impeachment vote |url=https://www.politico.com/news/2021/01/13/crow-condemns-taylor-greene-rhetoric-458705?fbclid=IwAR1eYHifWvj4NS-lAgqkudZQhny5MF7wJrsuGHxvNothTxfAqYxhjPx8IY0 |access-date=2021-01-29 |work=[[政客_(媒體)|政客]]|language=en|date=2021-01-13}}</ref>。

2021年1月21日，也就是[[乔·拜登|乔·拜登]]就职的第二天，格林提交了{{le|弹劾拜登的努力|Efforts to impeach Joe Biden|弹劾拜登的文件}}，指控拜登滥用职权<ref name="KxpJ8">{{cite magazine |url=https://www.newsweek.com/qanon-linked-congresswoman-file-impeachment-articles-against-biden-january-21-1561414 |title=QAnon-Linked Congresswoman to File Impeachment Articles Against Biden on January 21 |first1=Jeffery |last1=Martin |magazine=[[新聞周刊|新聞周刊]]|date=2021-01-13 |access-date=2021-01-29}}</ref>。在接受[[大全新闻|Newsmax]]记者格雷格·凯利采访时，她指责拜登“愿意滥用总统办公室的权力，很容易被外国政府、外国能源公司，包括中国能源公司和乌克兰能源公司收买。”<ref name="VUFea">{{cite news|last=Castronuovo|first=Celine|url=https://thehill.com/homenews/house/534178-marjorie-taylor-greene-says-she-will-introduce-impeachment-articles-against|title=Marjorie Taylor Greene says she will introduce impeachment articles against Biden|work=[[國會山報|國會山報]]|date=2021-01-13|access-date=2021-01-29}}</ref>

