===發布懷疑煽動暴力對待民主黨政要的圖片===
2020年9月3日，格林在她的Facebook页面上分享了一張圖片，她手持一把{{le|AR-15型步枪|AR-15 style rifle}}，旁边是民主党众议员[[亚历山德里娅·奥卡西奥-科尔特斯|亚历山德里娅·奥卡西奥-科尔特斯]]、[[伊尔汗·奥马尔|伊尔汗·奥马尔]]和[[拉希达·特莱布|拉希达·特莱布]]的照片拼贴。格林声称，现在是共和党人“对这些想把我们国家撕裂的社会主义者进行攻击的时候了”<ref>{{cite news|last1=Bade|first1=Rachael|last2=Wagner|first2=John|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/marjorie-taylor-greene-gun-squad-photo/2020/09/04/bb1da24c-eebc-11ea-b4bc-3a2098fc73d4_story.html|title=GOP candidate poses with rifle, says she's targeting 'socialist' congresswomen|work=The Washington Post|date=2020-09-04|access-date=2021-01-10|archive-date=2020-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200905021818/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/marjorie-taylor-greene-gun-squad-photo/2020/09/04/bb1da24c-eebc-11ea-b4bc-3a2098fc73d4_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。众议院议长[[南希·佩洛西|南希·佩洛西]]谴责这一圖片是“危险的暴力威胁”，奥马尔在声称这一圖片已经引发死亡威胁后，要求删除圖片。在回答《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》关于圖片是否构成威胁的问题时，格林竞选团队的一位发言人称这一建议“偏执且荒谬”，是一种“阴谋论”<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/jackbrewster/2020/09/03/trump-backed-qanon-candidate-posts-meme-showing-off-gun-and-urging-offense-against-aoc-the-squad/|title=Trump-Backed QAnon Candidate Posts Meme Showing Off Gun And Urging 'Going On The Offense' Against AOC, The Squad|first=Jack|last=Brewster|work=Forbes|date=2020-09-03|access-date=2021-01-10|archive-date=2020-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200905201035/https://www.forbes.com/sites/jackbrewster/2020/09/03/trump-backed-qanon-candidate-posts-meme-showing-off-gun-and-urging-offense-against-aoc-the-squad/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Facebook第二天删除了这一圖片，因为它违反了关于煽动暴力的政策，促使格林声称民主党“在我宣誓就职之前就想将我‘[[取消文化|取消]]’”<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.politico.com/news/2020/09/04/facebook-removes-candidates-squad-post-409175|title=Facebook removes QAnon-supporting candidate's 'squad' post for inciting violence|first1=Cristiano|last1=Lima|work=Politico|date=2020-09-04|access-date=2021-01-10|archive-date=2020-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200904223908/https://www.politico.com/news/2020/09/04/facebook-removes-candidates-squad-post-409175|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===散播校園槍擊案陰謀論和騷擾槍擊案生還者===
有媒體在2021年1月翻出格林先後在Facebook上發表了關於[[校園槍擊案|校園槍擊案]]的文章和回應，她認為[[桑迪胡克小學槍擊案|2012年桑迪胡克小學槍擊案]]及[[2018年佛羅里達校園槍擊案|2018年佛羅里達校園槍擊案]]都是反槍支人士所策劃的[[假旗行動|假旗行動]]，旨在將責任歸咎於[[美國公開持武權|持械法]]。在另一個2018年的發文中格林又寫道「我聽說[[南希·佩洛西|南希·佩洛西]]在一個月內多次告訴[[比爾·克林頓|比爾·克林頓]]說：『我們需要另一宗槍擊案』說服大眾要求更嚴格的槍械管制方案。」<ref name="SVNmI">{{cite news|last=Hananoki|first=Eric|url=https://www.mediamatters.org/false-flag-conspiracy-theory/rep-marjorie-taylor-greene-facebook-2018-parkland-school-shooting-was|title=Rep. Marjorie Taylor Greene on Facebook in 2018: Parkland school shooting was a false flag planned event|work=Media Matters for America|date=2021-01-19|access-date=2021-02-01}}</ref><ref name="0BLwa">{{Cite web|url=https://www.mediamatters.org/false-flag-conspiracy-theory/facebook-2018-rep-marjorie-taylor-greene-endorsed-conspiracy-theories|title=On Facebook in 2018, Rep. Marjorie Taylor Greene endorsed conspiracy theories that 9/11 was an inside job and that Sandy Hook was staged|first=Eric|last=Hananoki|website=Media Matters for America|date=2021-01-21|accessdate = 2021-02-01}}</ref>槍擊暴力事件中的生還者包括{{le|弗雷德·古滕伯格|Fred Guttenberg}}、{{le|戴维·霍格|David Hogg}}和{{le|卡梅隆·卡斯基|Cameron Kasky}}等人譴責格林的發言並要求她主動從眾議院辭職<ref name="r47Av">{{cite news|url=https://www.buzzfeednews.com/article/amberjamieson/marjorie-taylor-greene-parkland-false-flag|title=Parkland Survivors Want Marjorie Taylor Greene To Resign For Calling The Shooting A "False Flag"|author1=Amber Jamieson|work=BuzzFeed News|date=2021-01-19|accessdate = 2021-02-01}}</ref><ref name="Gz6Y0">{{cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/nation/2021/01/22/marjorie-taylor-greene-parkland-sandyhook/|title=Advocates push for Marjorie Taylor Greene's resignation over report that she spread falsehoods about school shootings|last=Salcedo|first=Andrea|work=The Washington Post|date=2021-01-22|accessdate=2021-02-01}}</ref>。其中霍格是佛羅里達校園槍擊案的生還者，自該事件起成為了遊說加強監管槍支的活躍分子，格林在社交媒體上稱呼他為「小[[阿道夫·希特勒|希特拉]]（{{lang|en|#littleHitler}}）」<ref name="cnn210126">{{Cite web |url = https://edition.cnn.com/2021/01/26/politics/marjorie-taylor-greene-democrats-violence/index.html|title = Marjorie Taylor Greene indicated support for executing prominent Democrats in 2018 and 2019 before running for Congress|website=CNN |author = Steck, Em; Kaczynski, Andrew|date = 2021-01-26|language = en|accessdate = 2021-02-01}}</ref>。格林在2019年3月發布過一段影片拍攝她在街道上尾隨霍格並不斷發言挑逗，指責他利用其它小孩子達成個人慾望，霍格全程對格林不理不睬。當格林停止跟隨霍格後對著鏡頭說霍格是一名膽小鬼，並指控他獲得金融家[[喬治·索羅斯|喬治·索羅斯]]金錢支助<ref>{{cite news|last=Marcos|first=Cristina|url=https://thehill.com/homenews/house/536118-video-shows-rep-marjorie-taylor-greene-calling-parkland-shooting-survivor-a|title=Video shows Rep. Greene calling Parkland shooting survivor a 'coward'|work=The Hill|date=2021-01-27|accessdate = 2021-02-01}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Gonzalez|first=Oriana|url=https://www.axios.com/david-hogg-marjorie-taylor-green-harassment-8fbfb81a-3745-40d3-973b-b5daca948d86.html|title=David Hogg: "I absolutely remember" Marjorie Taylor Greene harassment|work=Axios|date=2021-01-28|accessdate = 2021-02-01}}</ref>，霍格事後在接受新聞訪問中否認有收受索羅斯的錢財<ref>{{cite|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eCSoLCmJwOs|title=Parkland survivor responds to video of Marjorie Taylor Greene confronting him with baseless claims|publisher=有線新聞網YouTube頻道|date=2021-01-28|accessdate=2021-02-01}}</ref>。

有記者於2021年1月27日在市政廳向格林提問，關於她騷擾霍格的影片時有人威脅要報警逮捕該記者<ref>{{cite news |last1=O'Kane|first1=Caitlin|title=Reporter says she was threatened with arrest after trying to ask Rep. Marjorie Taylor Greene a question at town hall |url=https://www.cbsnews.com/news/marjorie-taylor-greene-town-hall-reporter-question/?ftag=CNM-00-10aab6a&linkId=110170629&fbclid=IwAR0cXIN33_AtKNoLsJYIM6E2s-0Gtec0TLDGPRVZkSPWNPXc45Hqx0XpxkU |access-date=2021-02-01 |work=cbsnews.com |publisher=CBS News |date=2021-01-27}}</ref>。

當格林對校園槍擊的發言和騷擾霍格的情報被翻出後，民主黨眾議員{{le|贾哈娜·海耶斯|Jahana Hayes}}向共和黨黨魁要求不要安排格林出任教育委員會<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.courant.com/politics/hc-pol-jahana-hayes-marjorie-taylor-greene-20210128-6mh4y37yvvh2zb66jqzn46ebmi-story.html|title=Rep. Jahana Hayes asks Georgia Rep. Marjorie Taylor Greene not be seated on House Education Committee after she questioned legitimacy of Sandy Hook shooting|author1=Michael Hamad|publisher=The Hartford Courant|date=2021-01-28|accessdate=2021-02-01}}</ref>。

===散播外太空裝置製造山火陰謀論===
2018年11月，格林的Facebook賬號分享了關於[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]][[營溪大火|營溪大火]]的陰謀論，發文指這場破當地紀錄的山火災害是由時任加州州長[[謝利·布朗|謝利·布朗]]、[[太平洋瓦電公司|太平洋瓦電公司]]、{{le|羅斯柴爾德集團|Rothschild & Co}}和[[太空太陽能|太空太陽能]]發電新興企業{{le|Solaren}}聯手策劃、利用「外太空太陽能發電機」人為引發的，目的是將特定區域燒盡給相關企業騰出空地發展<ref>{{Cite news|last=Hananoki|first=Eric|url=https://www.mediamatters.org/facebook/marjorie-taylor-greene-penned-conspiracy-theory-laser-beam-space-started-deadly-2018|title=Marjorie Taylor Greene penned conspiracy theory that a laser beam from space started deadly 2018 California wildfire|work=Media Matters for America|date=2021-01-28|access-date=2021-02-05}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Ting|first=Eric|url=https://www.sfgate.com/politics/amp/Marjorie-Taylor-Greene-California-wildfires-lasers-15906292.php|title=Marjorie Taylor Greene's nonsense theory about the Camp Fire, Jerry Brown and space lasers|work=SFGate|date=2021-01-28|access-date=2021-02-05}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Steinberg|first=Rachel|url=https://www.thejc.com/news/us/congresswoman-s-comments-linking-rothschilds-to-california-wildfires-prompt-mockery-and-outrage-1.511357|title=Congresswoman's comments linking Rothschilds to California wildfires prompt mockery and outrage|work=The Jewish Chronicle|date=2021-01-29|access-date=2021-02-05}}</ref>。陰謀論經常將[[羅斯柴爾德家族|羅斯柴爾德家族]]描述成「猶太裔國際金融黑幕」，其言論被指具有[[反猶太主義|反猶太主義]]而帶有歧視成分。格林的發文並沒有直接提及「猶太」，但於2021年1月不少媒體報導這發文時都以「猶太太空激光」來調侃格林<ref name="TooFab20210129">{{cite news|url=https://toofab.com/2021/01/29/jewish-space-laser-california-wildfires-marjorie-taylor-greene-solaren/|newspaper=TooFab|title=Owner of 'Jewish Space Laser' Hits Back at Marjorie Taylor Greene Claim it Started California Wildfire.|date=2021-01-29|accessdate=2021-02-05}}</ref><ref name="NW20210129">{{cite news|newspaper=[[新聞周刊|新聞周刊]]|title=Marjorie Taylor Greene's 'Jewish Space Lasers' Conspiracy Theory Met With Derision, Jokes|author-first=Jack|author-last=Dutton|url=https://www.newsweek.com/marjorie-taylor-greene-jewish-space-laser-mockery-1565325|date=2021-01-29|accessdate=2021-02-05}}</ref>。佛羅里達校園槍擊案死者父親弗雷德·古滕伯格回應這報導時指，他不覺得格林是在開玩笑，「她否認了我的女兒在槍擊案中被殺（...）但因為我的姓氏是古滕伯格，因為我是猶太人，她認為我對樹林發射了激光引致山火。<ref name="LAT20210130">{{cite news|newspaper=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]|title=Truth set ablaze by conspiracy theories|author1-first=Hailey|author1-last=Branson Potts|author2-first=Joseph|author2-last=Serna|author3-first=Alejandra|author3-last=Reyes-Velarde|date=2021-01-30|accessdate=2021-02-05}}</ref>」

Solaren於2021年1月發表聲明澄清，其[[太空太陽能|太空太陽能]]技術並不涉及以[[激光|激光]]將[[光學頻譜|光學頻譜]]中的[[可見光|可見光]]從太空向地球發射，所以不可能存在格林發文中指導致山火的「藍色光線」，其系統亦沒有利用激光傳送能量。至於Solaren與[[太平洋瓦電公司|太平洋瓦電公司]]的合約到2015年已經終止，而直至2021年Solaren都沒有發射任何人造衛星上太空<ref name="Solaren20210129">{{cite web|website=Solaren網站|url=https://www.solarenspace.com/2021/01/29/facebook-post-referencing-solaren-space-solar-setting-the-record-straight/|title=FACEBOOK POST REFERENCING SOLAREN SPACE SOLAR – SETTING THE RECORD STRAIGHT|date=2021-01-29|accessdate=2021-02-05}}</ref>。

===被Twitter永久封鎖個人帳戶===
2022年1月1日，格林在[[Twitter|Twitter]]發言，指美國出現不尋常地大量的疫苗相關死亡個案。其後，Twitter便以言論違反平台關於疫苗資訊正確性為由，宣布永久封鎖格林的個人帳戶，而Twitter平台稱曾4度因疫苗假資訊向格林發出警告。格林事後在另一社交通訊軟件[[Telegram|Telegram]]發出聲明，強調社交平台不能阻止真相傳播，批評Twitter幫助在「共產革命」（Communist revolution）的匿名敵人，Twitter的決定證明公司是「美國敵人」（a enemy to America）。<ref>[https://inews.hket.com/article/3145884/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E5%B1%A2%E7%99%BC%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E5%81%87%E8%B3%87%E8%A8%8A%20Twitter%E6%B0%B8%E4%B9%85%E5%B0%81%E9%8E%96%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%9C%BE%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1?mtc=20009 被指屢發疫苗假資訊 Twitter永久封鎖美國眾議員]，2022/01/03，香港經濟日報</ref>

==个人生活==
自2002年以来，格林和她的丈夫佩里共同拥有泰勒商业公司（{{lang|en|Taylor Commercial}}），这是一家位于[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]][[阿尔法勒特|阿尔法勒特]]的建筑公司<ref name="FXStabil11092020"/><ref>{{cite news |date=2019-06-11 |title=Republican announces bid for Congress |url=http://www.thecrier.net/news/article_a10d7fe2-8c95-11e9-ab42-f73e656a5b68.html |accessdate=2021-01-10 |newspaper=Dunwoody Crier |archive-date=2020-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200610042329/http://www.thecrier.net/news/article_a10d7fe2-8c95-11e9-ab42-f73e656a5b68.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她长期居住在阿尔法勒特，这里属于第六选区。虽然众议院议员只需居住在他们所代表的州，但格林在考虑竞选第十四选区后不久表示，当她确定下来在那里竞选后，她打算搬到那一地区<ref>{{cite news |first=Diane |last=Wagner |date=2019-12-09 |title=GOP candidate from outside the district eyeing Graves' Congressional seat |url=https://www.northwestgeorgianews.com/rome/news/local/gop-candidate-from-outside-the-district-eyeing-graves-congressional-seat/article_c8a4be70-1ac1-11ea-b192-bf6c7065f882.html |accessdate=2021-01-10 |newspaper=Rome News-Tribune |archive-date=2020-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200610042850/https://www.northwestgeorgianews.com/rome/news/local/gop-candidate-from-outside-the-district-eyeing-graves-congressional-seat/article_c8a4be70-1ac1-11ea-b192-bf6c7065f882.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她随后在第十四选区的[[保尔丁县_(佐治亚州)|保尔丁县]]附近买了一套房子<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.npr.org/2020/10/22/926538094/npr-podcast-monitors-georgia-woman-called-americas-qanon-candidate|title=NPR Podcast 'No Compromise' Spotlights America's 'QAnon Candidate'|first1=Lisa|last1=Hagen|first2=Chris|last2=Haxel|work=NPR|date=2020-10-22|access-date=2021-01-10|archive-date=2020-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022114554/https://www.npr.org/2020/10/22/926538094/npr-podcast-monitors-georgia-woman-called-americas-qanon-candidate|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在她宣誓就职时，已经搬到了同在第十四选区的[[罗马_(乔治亚州)|罗马]]<ref>[https://clerk.house.gov/member_info/olm-117.pdf Official member list] for 117th Congress</ref>。

